ComicInfo.Summary: George Washington, the first president of the United States and the one true vampire king, has stepped out of the shadows to take back America and remold it into something far more wicked. Now, James Sangster and son must find a way to stop the undead commander-in-chief, but at what cost? And will there even be an America left to save after he’s done with it?
